Clix

If you want to add to your project some php scripts that will be runned from cli mode, then its time to use Clix.
Clix will help you to organize those scripts in one place with the same interface and feauter like:

 - mapping command line argument to task variables
 - display help message for task when --help parameter will be passed
 - interactive mode
 - all parameters will be check if they are correct

HOW TO USE IT: run example cli.php file 

To display help:
    php cli.php HelloWord --help

To run task:
    php cli.php HelloWord firstname=Adam lastname=Smith --uppercase

To run interactive mode:
    php cli.php

To list all available task:
    php cli.php --list
